The paper deals with attacks on face recognition systems based on deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and cybersecurity (cs.CR) sub-categories. The use of adversarial generative nets also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques. Additionally, the paper proposes a method for creating "universal" sets of eyeglasses, which could involve artificial intelligence (cs.AI) approaches.
